<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-11248] Add hadoop configuration to disable Azure Filesystem metrics collection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-11248</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Today whenever Azure filesystem is used, metrics collection is enabled using class AzureFileSystemMetricsSystem. Metrics being collected includes bytes transferred and throughput.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In some situation, we do not want to collect metrics for Azure file system. E.g. for WebHCat server. We need to introduce a new configuration &quot;fs.azure.skip.metrics&quot; to disable metrics collection.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
